title: Obama in 50 states
text: Updated 1438 GMT (2138 HKT) May 11, 2015 Obama in 50 states 50 photos President Barack Obama, visiting Watertown, South Dakota, on Friday, May 8, shows off a note given to him by 11-year-old Rebecca Kelley. Rebecca had written him a letter asking him to visit South Dakota, which is the 50th state Obama has visited during his time in office. White House photographer Pete Souza highlights a picture from each state.
